# DAX Measures

### Average Close Price

```
Average Close Price = AVERAGE(Stock[Close])
```

### Highest Price

```
Highest Price = MAX(Stock[High])
```

### Lowest Price

```
Lowest Price = MIN(Stock[Low])
```

### Total Volume

```
Total Volume = SUM(Stock[Volume])
```

### Volatility

```
Volatility = AVERAGEX('SHEET1',DIVIDE([Highest Price]-[Lowest Price],[Lowest Price]))
